author: jof
title: small and swooshy
review:
Another of the 45p Daily Mirror giveaways.

Its like one of the air race planes & quite swooshy for small boys to zoom around.

Pros:
Yellow wing plates, couple of smoked clear, yellow, trans red & 4 white 2/3 cheeses.
A propellor if you don't have plenty of them already.

Cons:
Not really much to this set. could have done with an undercarriage (skateboard wheels type maybe)
